---
title: Chicken Marsala with Skillet Zucchini and Mushroom Pan-Sauce
description: We’ve taken this Italian classic and made it a zillion times easier. The whole family will love the combination of creamy mushroom sauce, tender chicken, and seasonal squash. And although there’s no wine to be found, all the flavors are there — we promise!
